  "text": "Our results regarding the relative performances of mIR and NIR were opposite to those of Bona et al. [CITATION_1] . However, this disagreement is not inexplicable in light of the differences between these studies and considering previous findings on the application of IR spectroscopy to food science. Further research and comparative studies are required to understand the root of the disagreement, thus taking another step towards turning efficient coffee fraud detection by nontargeted chemical analysis in a practical reality.",
